   LTE-Sim Helper RELEASE NOTES
=========================

This file contains LTE-Sim Helper release notes.

Release 0.7
===========

Availability
------------
This release is available in: http://code.google.com/p/lte-sim-helper/


Supported platforms
-------------------
tested on
       - Linux amd64 Ubuntu 12.04 with g++-4.6 and python 2.7

New user-visible features
-------------------------
  - Added support to Multi Cell scenarios.
  - The default scenarios SingleCellWithInterference and MultiCell were re-written to read the parameters from a configuration file.
  - Now the user doesn`t have to indicate the path to config.cfg anymore.


